  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nAfter regular sync, we can validate gossip blocks for a while (like 10 minutes in my case) then gossip block failed the validation at proposer index check:\r\n\r\n```\r\nconst supposedProposerIndex = epochCtx.getBeaconProposer(signedBlock.message.slot);\r\n    if (supposedProposerIndex !== signedBlock.message.proposerIndex) {\r\n      return ExtendedValidatorResult.reject;\r\n    }\r\n```",
